name: Spiral Flora
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D spiral sculpture, with abstracted Australian kangaroo paw flowers, for the festive season and #hen600k. It is an adaptation of my genesis mint on HEN, around #hen500k, Agog Spiral, which was one of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
